<item>
            <title>[SEC-983] NPE in AuthenticationTag</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SEC-983</link>
                <project id="10040" key="SEC">Spring Security</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Incomplete security principal initialization can cause a NPE inside the tag:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Sample JSP code:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;s:authentication property=&quot;principal.activeParent&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Stack trace:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;java.lang.NullPointerException&lt;br/&gt;
	at org.springframework.security.taglibs.authz.AuthenticationTag.doEndTag(AuthenticationTag.java:123)&lt;br/&gt;
	at jsp_servlet.&lt;em&gt;web_45_inf._jsp.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;index._jsp&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;tag5(&lt;/em&gt;_index.java:357)&lt;br/&gt;
	at jsp_servlet.&lt;em&gt;web_45_inf._jsp.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;index._jspService(&lt;/em&gt;_index.java:143)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Fix:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Change AuthenticationTag.java line 123 to:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;writeMessage(result);&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;And line 128 to:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;protected void writeMessage(Object msg) throws JspException {&lt;/p&gt;</description>
